name: Worthless Two
description: Worthless 2.0 is a community-driven revival and reimagination of the original Worthless token, which was abandoned by its creators. The community took ownership, rebuilt the token with a fresh contract, and renewed focus on transparency and decentralization. Worthless 2.0 is designed to empower holders through collective action and to foster a fun, fair, and engaged community without any presales or team allocations.
